data.description: This stunning property has been meticulously maintained with a host of modern features, the main level offers beautiful hardwood floors with open floor plan with grand entry way. Office with french doors that can also can be use as a dining area, gorgeous chefs kitchen with custom cabinetry and quartz island with stainless steel appliances that opens up to the large family room. Bonus/Flex room that can be used for multiply use and a large half baths. Outside, you'll find a well-manicured fenced in yard and lush landscaping that provides the perfect backdrop for outdoor entertaining and relaxation. Upstairs offers a  beautiful loft that can be use for the media room or playroom and 4 large bedrooms 2 full baths.  Washer and Dryer included and home also offers upgraded lighting and ceiling fans throughout. This home is like new. Ask about the assumable mortgage rate.
